15623.title: Good Dick
15623.description: A neurotic video store clerk is enamored with a quiet woman who rents adult films, but her traumatic past has left her uninterested in a relationship.

294335.title: First Beautiful Thing
294335.description: The First Beautiful Thing follows a strong and optimistic mother raising her two children against all odds.

304797.title: Benny & Joon
304797.description: A quirky, romantic drama about two misfits who come together as a result of an unusual poker game.

305027.title: Stay Hungry
305027.description: Jeff Bridges and Sally Field star in this quirky, sensitive drama about a wealthy Southern bachelor who learns that money and charm have their limitations.  Arnold Schwarzenegger also appears.

305836.title: Romance & Cigarettes
305836.description: In this romantic musical comedy, a husband’s life unravels as he pursues a relationship with a younger woman and reflects on his life choices.

321562.title: Janeane From Des Moines
321562.description: Janeane Wilson is a conservative Iowa housewife looking for a Republican leader to defeat Barack Obama in 2012 and take America back from illegal immigrants, Planned Parenthood and Obamacare. She dives into Iowa Tea Party politics and the lead-up to the 2012 presidential race, but a crumbling economy causes her to lose everything she holds dear -- her job, her marriage, her health, and her home. As Mitt Romney and the GOP front-runners criss-cross Iowa during her hour of need, Janeane faces some very dark realizations. Will any of the candidates hear her story or answer her questions? Part cautionary tale, part tragic-comedy, JANEANE FROM DES MOINES is about a true believer whose faith is severely tested.

321870.title: Roger Dodger
321870.description: A charismatic but troubled man guides his 16-year-old nephew through New York City's nightlife for an all-night crash course in the art of seduction.

327419.title: Shotgun Garfunkel
327419.description: South Africa's attempt at creating the fastest feature film ever made. A group of friends in their thirties go on the quest for an epic night out, opening the door to betrayal, lies, honesty and love.

329427.title: Dream a Little Dream
329427.description: Coleman, an aging man desperately searching for a way to prolong his life and that of his wife, Gena, switches brains with a teenager, Bobby Kelle.

341544.title: Roxie
341544.description: A coming-of-age film about two sixty-year-old best buddies who should have come-of-age a long time ago.

389516.title: Fort Tilden
389516.description: In this quirky comedy, two teenage girls trek to the beach to meet up with guys, taking a circuitous journey with very little idea how to get there.

394216.title: The Way You Are
394216.description: Following the send-off on her last working day, callous judge Helene Offer, under the influence of alcohol, causes a car accident with grave consequences.To save her reputation, she takes care of the victim's daughter, Michalina, who suffers from Down syndrome. With her spontaneity and warmth, Michalina turns Helene's lonesomelife upside down and has her reconsidering her relationship with her estranged son Rupert. And the young woman needs help with an impossible plan. She wants to marry her boyfriend, Sebastian,who also suffers from Down syndrome. And that is legally impossible. Helene attends to the matter and against official and family resistance attempts to make possible a church wedding for the unusual couple. Through her commitment to Michalina, Helene finds an unexpected way back to her son Rupert.

445664.title: Red Ribbon Blues
445664.description: In this unique tale of modern day vigilantism, a group of activists declare war against the drug company establishment. This HIV support group turned warriors are determined to receive the attention and treatment they feel they are being denied, and plan a heist to steal the medication that they need.

449818.title: Uncle Nino
449818.description: A Chicago family in a state of crisis gets a chance to come together when their estranged uncle from a small town in Italy pays them a surprise visit.

461273.title: Last Call at Murrays
461273.description: Client losses and smoking laws force a man to close his karaoke bar, but a freak blizzard strands a group of strangers who set off a chain of events.

461516.title: Flourish
461516.description: A woman desperate for cash agrees to agree a rebellious, smart-aleck teen. When the girl disappears, an amusing and dangerous search takes place.

461520.title: On the Road With Judas
461520.description: An author's reality blends with his fiction, or perhaps his fiction blends with his reality, as his writing process becomes more convoluted.

461542.title: Going Nomad
461542.description: A grown man, living in New York and going nowhere in life, tries to find his purpose and live up to his mother’s expectations, in this witty dramedy.

463176.title: Jerico
463176.description: The story of best friends who set out on a dangerous, but comedic journey that challenges the restrictions of a Jim Crow South to fulfill their dreams

463193.title: Desastres Naturales
463193.description: Raquel, a teacher who refuses to accept the idea retiring, arrives at her classroom only to discover she has been replaced with a much younger teacher. Raquel rejects this idea and proceeds with her lecture. The students occupy a classroom and rally behind their former teacher with a small revolt that threatens the establishment's order.

465007.title: Crazy Mama
465007.description: An evicted mother (Ann Sothern) and daughter (Cloris Leachman) lead a cross-country 1950s crime spree.

465177.title: For Now
465177.description: Two orphaned, grieving siblings and their twenty-something pals take a road trip along the California coast that forces them to face uncertainty.

467314.title: Headed South for Christmas
467314.description: An angst-ridden teen longs to meet the mother who died during her birth, as her dad takes her to spend Christmas with relatives they barely know.

468028.title: All I Want
468028.description: Friends gather for a couple's 10-year wedding anniversary, only to discover that everything they thought about their relationship is wrong.

468340.title: The Middle of X
468340.description: A grad night party thrown by high school sweethearts ends tragically for a circle of friends who reunite in midlife for a night of nostalgic reality.

468452.title: Good Enough
468452.description: When her father passes away, a flight attendant based in New York embarks on a quest to find a long-lost relative and makes an astonishing discovery.

469941.title: Made for Each Other
469941.description: When a rising young lawyer marries a girl he's only known for one day, their love is tested by his disapproving boss and family and a baby on the way.

470329.title: Walter
470329.description: Walter doesn't just rip tickets at the movie theater. Thanks to a pact with God, he also gets to decide the eternal fates of everyone he meets.

470739.title: 6 Non Smokers
470739.description: Dr. Henry Caldwell, the world's foremost mediator, faces the biggest challenge of his career when he takes on six roommates whose only thing in common is that none of them smoke.

475182.title: Bitter Melon
475182.description: A Filipino-American family in San Francisco abused by an older brother get caught up in the youngest brother’s plan to murder him at Christmas.

476747.title: Tucked
476747.description: When a 74-year-old drag queen receives a diagnosis with six weeks left to live, he must make peace with his daughter and perform one final act.

479069.title: The Flesh (Italian)
479069.description: A divorced musician who is the sex slave of a powerful bombshell he’s fallen in love with is determined not to let her go even when she tires of him.

485567.title: Friends Forever
485567.description: Six friends get together for an annual reunion where secrets are revealed and lives are reexamined in this comedy about the darker side of growing up.

485848.title: Bone
485848.description: Welcome to Beverly Hills, where upper class white married couples like Bill and Bernadette enjoy their happy life of wealth and privelege. But when a violently unstable black criminal invades their home, each will be forced to explore their own nightmares of lies and desire where every perverse secret is exposed and nothing is ever really black and white.

486060.title: Listen Up Philip
486060.description: When a self-obsessed novelist (Jason Schwartzman) has problems with his novel and his girlfriend (Elisabeth Moss), he seeks refuge in his mentor's cottage where the peace and quiet allow him to focus on his favorite subject - himself.

486538.title: Billboard
486538.description: Times are tough, listener-ship is down and Casey needs to come up with a plan to save his radio station, WTYT 960, and fast! Casey's grand plan is to host a billboard sitting contest, where four lucky contestants have the opportunity to win "nine-sixty thousand dollars and a mobile home". All they have to do is be the last person to survive, living on a billboard

489601.title: Everything Is Wonderful
489601.description: Two women take a week off from their hectic lives, to forget about their everyday burdens. But their friendship quickly evolves to a new territory.

490855.title: Merely Players
490855.description: After college, a man and his musician best friend collaborate musically. The album is a hit, but the friend bails until he needs help years later.

490888.title: The Lobster Kid
490888.description: When a teenage con artist and a monk join forces, anything is possible. Delve into this thoughtful, unusual, slice-of-life portrayal.

492610.title: The Comedians
492610.description: Two friends turn on each other when a magic ring presents the opportunity to become wealthy. Will they overcome their greedy instincts?

493331.title: The Three-Way Wedding
493331.description: A playwright gathers his mistress, his ex-wife and her lover together at a country home for a performance of his new play.

493896.title: Lost & Found
493896.description: An Irish train station connects 7 strangers, including a new employee, a beggar, and a woman ready to have a wedding, despite unusual circumstances.

495473.title: Sex Is a Four Letter Word
495473.description: A group of friends come to grips with their own experiences of four-letter words like love, lies and lust, in this romantic comedy set in Australia.

497135.title: Divine Will
497135.description: Will Blessing and his uncle Dave grace the town of Punkyville, Kentucky with their gifts of music, faith, and a renewed sense of hope.

497914.title: Accidents Happen
497914.description: When a teen rebels against his dysfunctional and unusually unlucky family, his pranks produce tragic results, yet reveal a bit of life’s magic.

499262.title: Ciudad en Celo
499262.description: Un grupo de amigos se encuentra solo y consciente de que, si quieren encontrar a alguien a quien amar, prestan más atención a sus sentimientos.

500477.title: Vacation!
500477.description: Four college girlfriends reunite for a vacation on the beach to drink and party, but a random drug buy causes a much different and tragic trip.

502877.title: What Now, Catherine Curtis?
502877.description: After many years of marriage to a philandering spouse, a divorcee struggles to begin life anew, and finds herself torn between two very different men.

505822.title: Sick of It All
505822.description: An eccentric and hilarious take on childhood, the loss of innocence adulthood brings, and zany schemes where sometimes children are the wisest.

507358.title: I'd Like to Be Alone Now
507358.description: A man grieving the deaths of his wife and three kids in a car crash nails his bedroom door shut when his family descends on his home with their chaos.

508329.title: Summer Fantasy
508329.description: Summer isn't all that’s hot when a high school grad gets a job as a lifeguard in LA and falls desperately in love with a much older lifeguard.

513428.title: Caido del Cielo (Doblado)
513428.description: Dos pasajeros de un avión accidentado llegan al hogar de una pareja que está criando a un hijo discapacitado.

513941.title: Me
513941.description: A delusional man, who believes that he’s the star of his own reality show, hires an actress to make his life more interesting and increase ratings.

514159.title: Detours
514159.description: A recently single New Yorker has to take a road trip South to her new Florida home with her widowed father holding her mom’s ashes in a coffee can.

516301.title: The Week
516301.description: Dick Romans is a washed-up TV host. When his wife leaves him before their 10-year anniversary, he decides to celebrate by himself.

517523.title: Wake.
517523.description: The lonely life of a mortician and agoraphobic grieving from the loss of her husband gets an odd restart with a new life-sized male doll named Pedro.

521591.title: Paparazzi Princess: The Paris Hilton Story
521591.description: Heiress-socialite Paris Hilton becomes a reality TV star and Hollywood club fixture until she is sent to the L.A. County Jail and has to rebrand.

521990.title: The Summer Before
521990.description: Between high school and college, two friends get jobs at a summer camp they attended as kids, where their bond and views of life and love are tested.

522146.title: Dogpound Shuffle
522146.description: An ex-vaudevillian recruits a wandering prizefighter to join in misadventures, as they try to raise enough money to spring his dog from the pound.

526330.title: Diamond Eye: T.H.O.T. Process 2
526330.description: A man’s hustle in life that willingly preys on the weaknesses of insecure women backfires and causes him to become homeless, broke, and friendless.

526774.title: After Love
526774.description: After 15 years of marriage, Marie and Boris decide to call it quits but Boris can't afford to move out and their household becomes a war zone.

528713.title: The Mafia Kills Only in Summer
528713.description: The Cosa Nostra’s reign of crime in 1970s Sicily unfolds through the eyes of a young boy obsessed with both the Mafia and his schoolmate crush.

529355.title: Delirious: Official Director’s Cut
529355.description: A paparazzi hires a homeless kid as his assistant.

530689.title: Someone to Love
530689.description: On Valentine’s Day, a Hollywood film director assembles a group of friends and strangers in a movie theater and interviews them about love and loneliness.

530691.title: Eating
530691.description: A multi-generational group of women gather for a birthday party and discuss their lives and the food they cook for men and themselves.

531739.title: The Dunning Man
531739.description: When Connor returns to Atlantic City to rebuild his life with income from his condos, he suddenly finds himself in a world of trouble.

541391.title: 10E
541391.description: Widower Robert realizes his best may not be good enough in raising his 17-year-old daughter when her reputation takes a massive hit just before prom.

543129.title: Reach
543129.description: Social outcast Steven is planning to take his own life. Until he befriends a free-spirited new student at school, who inspires him to reconsider.

546211.title: The Book That Wrote Itself
546211.description: A writer thinks he’s created a great novel about Irish life. When his book is rejected, he films it and tries to pitch the A-list at a film festival.

548164.title: Tradition
548164.description: On his last day on the bench, a district court judge finds himself presiding over the most controversial case his court and his town have ever seen.

548350.title: People With Issues
548350.description: Three friends, including two musicians and a cartoonist with a new lease on life, try to tame their  personal demons and stay creatively ambitious.

564063.title: Lift
564063.description: A man’s life is about to take a wild and amazing turn over the course of one night when he sets off for work as a driver for a ridesharing app.

564098.title: Abe
564098.description: A boy with Israeli and Palestinian family that are always at odds tries to bring unity by way of a perfect meal after he is mentored by a gifted chef.

564210.title: After the Reality
564210.description: A bachelor on a hit reality TV dating show must face real life after his father dies and he quits the show to reunite with his overwhelmed sister.

566395.title: The Crowded Day
566395.description: A group of young women work together at a department store and share residence in a hostel while surviving the ups and downs of life in the 1950s.

572381.title: Cheer Up
572381.description: When a group of girls considered social outcast decide to compete with the preppy's they ask the help of their aunt and they all go on a roller coaster ride of fun,growth and winning.

572686.title: Tribu
572686.description: Five businesswomen try to act like they don’t secretly despise one another while hosting a benefit for children in Africa at a high-end restaurant.

574746.title: Tomorrow La Scala
574746.description: A British opera troupe works together with prisoners at a maximum security facility to put on a rushed production of Stephen Sondheim’s Sweeney Todd.

575258.title: I'll Be Around
575258.description: Post-punk music festival attendees find themselves questioning their life choices as a variety of conflicts reminds them of their limitations.

579218.title: Let Me Buy You a Drink
579218.description: An Italian Millennial, whose plans to be an MMA fighter hit the wall, returns to Italy to face his new reality with his family and closest friends.

585908.title: By the Wayside
585908.description: A background actor struggling to get his big break and his three friends indulge in a life-awakening lost weekend of drinking, drugs, and sex.

586473.title: Half Empty/Half Full
586473.description: Secrets, truth, and a brutal change awaits friends who reunite for a night of catching up on each other’s lives - before they shatter each other.

589468.title: Nasty Baby
589468.description: Standing in the way of a gay male couple and their friend trying to conceive a baby is a pestering neighbor who may be more dangerous than he appears.

590488.title: Senior Love Triangle
590488.description: When a WWII veteran meets and falls for two women in a California retirement home, he goes on a mission to save them from their loneliness.

596141.title: Expecting Mary
596141.description: Expecting Mary is the story of a young girl who's had all the trappings of an upscale life, but it's only when she finds herself in a downtrodden trailer park in a small New Mexico town that she learns the real meaning of love, sacrifice, and family.

596567.title: Son of Clowns
596567.description: A TV actor must return to his North Carolina hometown and live with his parents, as he watches his ideals of life come tumbling down.

596608.title: Four Walls
596608.description: This slice-of-life drama offers a realistic look into the changing relationships experienced by a group of people over the course of a single day.

599074.title: Oh Lucy!
599074.description: When her English-instructor John suddenly disappears from class, Setsuko travels halfway around the world in search of him to the outskirts of Southern California.

599261.title: The Midnight Orchestra
599261.description: After leaving Morocco amidst racial tensions spurred by the Yom Kippur war, the son of a once famous Jewish musician travels to his home country to bury his father. As he meets the members of the band, his life unexpectedly transforms.

600341.title: Double Belgian
600341.description: Lifelong friends Brett and Mitchell travel to New York City to secure an investment for their upstate New York brewery. Once in the city, however, a hidden agenda and secret love interest threaten to derail their plans.

601136.title: Life With Father
601136.description: In 1880s New York, a curmudgeonly stockbroker demands the strictest order in his household. But his wife and four sons have demands of their own.

602927.title: Between the Lines
602927.description: In the first era of the fading counterculture press during the late ‘60s and early 70s, an underground Boston newspaper faces a corporate buyout.

603093.title: Flags on the Field
603093.description: Four Georgia friends deal with life’s challenges together, tackling the obstacles of friendship, family life, betrayal, and more.

603144.title: Andie the Great
603144.description: After dropping out of college, a young woman moves back in with her parents and attempts to figure out her new identity with old friends.

603302.title: Dust
603302.description: A dysfunctional family of three eccentric and stubborn siblings fall down a rabbit hole of tragic and comical consequences over their family home.

604588.title: Before/During/After
604588.description: Jennie Lonergan figures out the kind of person she wants to be when her 15-year marriage comes to an end.

605607.title: Ellie Parker
605607.description: Naomi Watts brings to life the madcap and hilarious series of struggles of a woman trying to have a Hollywood acting career on her own terms.

607284.title: Grown Men
607284.description: A meditation on what it means to be a man as a group of five old friends spend the night telling stories that betray their arrested development.

608644.title: All About Nina
608644.description: After moving to Los Angeles, a stand up comic finds her love life getting complicated just as her career is about to move up to the next level.

613116.title: Corazón Marchito
613116.description: Una amistad de toda la vida se somete a una prueba de fuego con las presiones propias de llegar a la edad de los treinta y tantos.

614782.title: Mama Weed
614782.description: A translator with the Paris police (Isabelle Huppert) finds herself in possession of a huge store ofhash, the insider knowledge required to move it and an unexpected flair for the danger that ensues.

615342.title: Welcome to the Men's Group
615342.description: A men's support group descends into chaos when long standing conflicts threaten the trust between the men.

615890.title: Days of Bagnold Summer
615890.description: A teenager spends his summer listening to heavy metal music and trying to get along with his librarian mom.

619821.title: Bloody Lip
619821.description: In this mockumentary, a pro fighter tries to get into shape in a short amount of time in order to square off against his boyhood nemesis.

620902.title: Mrs. Henderson Presents
620902.description: A recently widowed woman uses her money and clout to open up a London theater and hire young women to perform scandalous, all-nude revues.

621899.title: Tick Tock Lullaby
621899.description: Follow the missteps of a same-sex couple with baby fever as they hatch a variety of desperate plans to pin down just the right sperm donor.

626795.title: A Reel Life
626795.description: In this surreally dark comedy indie, a screenwriter’s latest screenplay starts to merge into reality, confusing his grasp on what’s true and fantasy.

627775.title: Hey Hey It's Esther Blueburger
627775.description: Inspiring comedy film about a quirky and fun private school teen who makes a public-school friend and secretly enrolls as a foreign exchange student.

627911.title: Witches
627911.description: When three high-powered friends spend time together, they share nights filled with laughter, drama, anger, and a strong friendship.

628020.title: Between Us
628020.description: The darkly comic tale of two couples, who reunite over two incendiary evenings, when love, marriage, dreams, disappointment, and friendship collide.

629840.title: Sopranos Bloopers, Home Movies, & Rare Footage
629840.description: Fans of “The Sopranos” will love this collection of segments, bloopers, premiere events and more, featuring the iconic crime show’s beloved cast.

630627.title: For Sale by Owner
630627.description: One wild, unusual day of trying to sell his deceased father's used van brings a grieving son in contact with the craziest group of buyers imaginable.

631421.title: Accidentally Dad
631421.description: A doctor’s life changes when he literally runs into a one-night-stand who says he’s the father of her cute and headstrong daughter–except he’s not.

631501.title: Ghar Sansar
631501.description: A man whose father dies is forced to choose between selling off their family estate to pay off his father’s debts or work them off over time.

632903.title: Before You Know It
632903.description: Set in early ‘90’s New York City, a pair of codependent sisters learn the mother they were told was dead is alive and starring in a popular soap opera.

633117.title: Stalled
633117.description: A fish out of water tale challenging preconceptions about “rednecks” for a Chicago rock band when van troubles leave them stranded in rural Alabama.

634518.title: Guy
634518.description: When a young journalist learns he’s the illegitimate son of a famous but aging French pop singer, he poses as a documentarian to follow him on tour.

634848.title: The Decline of the American Empire
634848.description: Sexual revelations emerge, when a group of academics from the University of Montreal and their partners spend a weekend at a country retreat.

635601.title: Shake Off the World
635601.description: After getting sidelined by his coach, Austin goes from a rising football star to the new bullied kid on the block attending a different high school.

639317.title: Samba
639317.description: Romance blossoms between an undocumented Senegalese immigrant working in Paris and the insomniac caseworker trying to keep him in the country.

640112.title: Tyrel
640112.description: A friends’ weekend retreat takes a disastrous turn for the only member of the group who is Black, who begins to feel like he’s being targeted.

640451.title: A Practical Guide to a Spectacular Suicide
640451.description: A suicidal twenty-something man has made many attempts to end his life, but decides if he wants to truly end things, he must go out in a big way.

640710.title: Nora's Will
640710.description: Nora, ex esposa de José, murió justo antes de Pascua y, al quedarse con el cuerpo por un tiempo, se da cuenta de que ella dejó un plan para la familia.

641810.title: Cowboy.Mov
641810.description: Burdened with financial debt and the estrangement of his son, fast food worker Travis Howell finds refuge by channeling his overnight meme status into an increasingly dangerous and powerful online conspiracy show.

647383.title: You’re Gonna Miss Me

653242.title: Six Weeks to Twelve Years
653242.description: After the death of their abusive dad, two estranged twins reunite to sell off his property and learn he wasn’t exactly the man he presented to them.

655726.title: Butter
655726.description: Witness the directorial debut of Alan Cumming, which follows a young woman living with an eating disorder, battling day-to-day difficulties.

657108.title: Animals
657108.description: An acclaimed independent film about a fiercely strong friendship between two party girls whose bond is shaken when one falls in love.

659579.title: Faceblocked
659579.description: When an Atlantic City woman suspects her longterm boyfriend of cheating, she and her friends hatch a catfishing scheme to catch him in the act.

660159.title: Four Cousins and a Christmas

661151.title: The Man with Hare Ears
661151.description: Josef is convinced that nothing can surprise him anymore, until one evening, he gets caught up in a series of events that turn his world upside-down.

667016.title: The Enormity of Life
667016.description: A suicidal man's life turns around when he receives a substantial inheritance and meets a charming single mom with a spirited daughter.

667956.title: The Young Poisoner's Handbook
667956.description: Inspired by the true story of a British teen with a morbid curiosity about chemically induced murder who allegedly poisoned those closest to him.

669059.title: Electric Jesus
669059.description: When a promoter sells a Christian metal band on the promise of a summer tour, their desire to "make Jesus famous" encounters numerous complexities.

669901.title: Cold Brook
669901.description: Two ordinary maintenance workers in a small town embark on an extraordinary adventure, risking everything for a stranger who needs their help.

673629.title: Then She Found Me
673629.description: April Epner, a schoolteacher, experiences heartbreak and loss while taking an improbable path toward personal fulfillment in her life.

676160.title: Love & Brotherhood
676160.description: After 5 years as a couple, Brandon and Makaila have decided to move in together. But there's a catch: Makaila's brother also needs a place to stay.

676867.title: Eeb Allay Ooo
676867.description: A young migrant employed by the government as a monkey repeller battles hordes of monkeys in the heart of New Delhi now that langurs are banned.

677037.title: If You See My Mother

680250.title: The Winning Season

681404.title: A Christmas Invitation
681404.description: It's Christmas, and a dysfunctional family is brought together through a dying wish and an invitation to one last family holiday party.

681754.description: This comedic fantasia is about a young man who works as a Michael Jackson impersonator and moves to a commune full of celebrity impersonators alike.

682113.title: Hobson's Choice
682113.description: Widower Henry Hobson is a successful bootmaker and a tyrannical father of three daughters who all want to leave him by getting married.

683393.title: Rollers
683393.description: A closet alcoholic with only one thing left to live for: Rollers. Now the venue is in trouble and he's running out of ways to save it and himself.

683755.title: Starf*cker
683755.description: A narcissistic psychopath with ADHD, BPD, and sex addiction tries to sleep his way to the top of Hollywood, only to find his world crashing down.

683987.description: Claudio es un forastero que llega a la ciudad de Quetzaltenango en Guatemala para despejarse hablando con su único amigo de confianza.

684021.description: With the looming fear of the apocalypse, Sadie must prepare herself in two weeks by mastering survival skills...all while going to high school.

684760.description: Three thirty-something friends struggle with their personal growth, families and relationships as they enter their second phase of life.

684901.title: Pol: Una Aventura en La USAC
684901.description: Pol, una chica de 14 y Flaco se esconden de un bravucón y su pandilla en un campus universitario mientras buscan un documento perdido.

691048.title: Ten Tricks
691048.description: Over the course of an evening, the city's most glamorous madam makes a pregnancy plan while the magician across the street makes a drastic move.

693396.title: Mallard's Road
693396.description: Three lost Lakota tribe members come together in a comedy of errors in their journey of discovery about what really matters in love and life.

701204.title: Bad Pastors
701204.description: Two unqualified Pastors switch churches in an attempt to steal money from their members. Will they get caught and change their ways?

702670.title: Bellas De Noche
702670.description: Un boxeador retirado entra a trabajar en un centro nocturno donde se enamora de una de las bailarinas y tiene que lidiar con varios personajes.

703995.title: Baked Bean
703995.description: After many dates with the wrong matches, Bertha sees in her colleague, Laura, a chance for true love while managing her mother’s encroaching dementia.

706701.title: Risk: The Life of Floyd and Sabrina
actors: Tia Big Momma Bad Azz Williams
706701.description: Follows the unbelievably rocky first six months in the lives and marriage of two newlyweds dogged by doubts, growing pains and past entanglements.

707359.title: Lovely & Amazing
707359.description: Self-esteem and insecurity lie at the heart of this comedy about the relationship between a mother and her three confused adult daughters.

707771.title: Cinema Donkey
707771.description: All that stands between a production crew’s lofty goal of making a film with a message for the whole of humanity is access to a professional donkey.

708797.title: Atlantafornication
708797.description: A man's peaceful suburban life is disrupted when he unexpectedly receives a large inheritance and his wife starts scheming for control of the money.

712089.title: Gasman
712089.description: Divorced, in debt and waiting for his big break, a self-sabotaging theater actor is offered the role of a Nazi hunting Jews with a mobile gas chamber.

712151.title: Family House
712151.description: The brother-in-law they haven’t heard from since his wife’s death last year suddenly shows up uninvited to the Denom family's annual weekend getaway.

715913.title: Common Ground
715913.description: This fun coming-of-age film details the struggles college students face when dealing with mental health issues.

716406.title: Meeting Venus
716406.description: A young Hungarian conductor's big break is threatened by difficult divas, striking dancers, feuding management, and an unexpected love interest.

716409.title: With Honors
716409.description: A homeless man holds a stuffy Ivy League student's misplaced graduate thesis hostage in return for room and board - one page for every day.

720865.title: Staycation
720865.description: A married couple on the edge of divorce is given a homework assignment from their marriage counselor to spend three days alone together in a house.

724582.title: A Little Help
724582.description: After her cheater husband’s heart gives out, a dental hygienist gets entangled in a run of bizarre lies in order to take care of her 12-year-old kid.

726021.title: The Perfect Gift
726021.description: Married couple Michael and Sandra find their festive holiday turning into chaos when both their parents come to visit unannounced.

100000618.title: Piensa en Mí (Doblado)
100000618.description: Una extraña historia de un cirujano cuya vida parece perfecta hasta que de repente descubre que solo le quedan un par de meses de vida.

100000845.title: Looking for Eric
100000845.description: In this hilarious romantic comedy, a soccer fanatic teams up with his hero to win back the woman he loves and save his son from gangsters.

100001374.title: Return of the Secaucus 7
100001374.description: A group of old college pals that were arrested together en route to an anti-war march at the Pentagon reunite over a summer weekend in New Hampshire.

100001632.title: Support Group Olympus
100001632.description: The Greek gods have fallen from grace and live among humans. When Ares ends up in jail, the gods are forced to participate in group therapy sessions.

100001954.title: Locas Y Atrapadas
100001954.description: Cinco mujeres quedan atrapadas en un ascensor y se confiesan las amargas experiencias que los hombres dominicanos les provocan en sus vidas.

100002256.title: Monkey Warfare
100002256.description: Two pot-smoking ex-revolutionaries living off the grid are thrown for a loop by their new dealer, who tries to rekindle their radical spirit.

100002443.title: London Fever
100002443.description: Two young men searching for a better life will stop at nothing to achieve their plan of going to London—including fleecing anyone who cares to listen.

100002636.title: Midnight Diner
100002636.description: Follows the stories of the regulars at a restaurant—that serves only from midnight until dawn—and the enigmatic owner and chef, who patiently listens.

100002980.title: Santorini Blue
100002980.description: When their marriage falls apart after a betrayal, Alexandra jets off to Greece while her husband becomes determined to rekindle their spark.

100003070.title: Just Can't Get Enough
100003070.description: This sexy drama spanning the decadent techno-dance era of the 80s chronicles the rise and fall of the original Chippendales nightclub.

100003115.title: Gimme the Loot
100003115.description: Two fledgling graffiti artists make a high-stakes gamble that a risky scheme will turn them into the most famous street artists in New York City.

0300008411.title: La Aprendiz (Doblado)
0300008411.description: Al morir el cuidador de su abuela, una estudiante de medicina decide especializarse en medicina legal y compensa su inexperiencia con una gran empatía.

0300006649.title: Miúdo Graúdo (Doblado)
0300006649.description: Miguelito es un pequeño genio de 11 años que desarrolló un proyecto secreto dentro de su propia habitación: una máquina que puede comunicarse con el futuro. Después de dedicar bastante tiempo y esfuerzo a mejorar su invento, el pequeño científico logra completar la primera conexión y charlar, brevemente, con alguien del futuro el mismo ... solo 20 años mayor

0300008649.title: Complicated
0300008649.description: Striving to leave their mark on a male-driven society, three millennials embark on a journey of love, sex, and betrayal, while navigating life’s road.

0300006429.title: Totally Frank
0300006429.description: Four very different but equally ambitious real-life twentysomething musicians pursue their far-reaching dream of becoming a successful band.

0300007994.title: Entitled
0300007994.description: Three off-the-rails adult children juggle grief, joy, and a mystery when their grumpy father leaves them a whopping inheritance they didn’t know of.

0300005087.title: Lockie Leonard
0300005087.description: Facing another year in the middle of nowhere, surf rat Lockie makes the best of small-town life with his friends and semi-functional family.

02175.title: In Your Dreams
02175.description: Australian teenage twins, Samantha and Ben Hazelton discover what ‘culture shock’ is all about when they spend the summer with their eccentric, aristocratic and accident prone relatives who live in a remote German castle.

0300007312.title: Sexless
0300007312.description: A group of friends, composed of two adult virgins and two celibate women, navigate maintaining their intimate relationships while abstaining from sex.

0300006994.title: Casting the Net
0300006994.description: Three actresses in L.A. having trouble getting roles take charge of their careers by putting out a fake casting call for an all-female Black Western.

01508.title: Packed to the Rafters
01508.description: Packed To The Rafters is a drama-comedy that turns a microscope on the lives of would-be empty-nesters Dave and Julie Rafter. Less than forty-eight hours after their reluctant middle son moves himself next door, all dreams of freedom and personal fulfilment are put on hold as one by one their youngest son and his princess wife, troubled eldest daughter and Julie's emotionally vulnerable father return to the family house. Ensuring that once again they are literally packed to the rafters.

0300004779.title: Grafters
0300004779.description: Two English brothers with different, clashing personalities become live-in home renovators for a notoriously finicky couple with strong opinions.
